productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Germaine has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks red.
The box this comes in is 3 inch by 6 centimeter and weights 15 ounce!
i use it centenially when i'm in my greenhouse.
My co-worker Knute has one of these. He says it looks smoky.
heard about this on brazilian radio, decided to give it a try.
